<og:description>A few months ago I thought it would be cool to use some of my RasPiO InsPiRing LEDs to make some indicators (turn signals) for my bicycle. But then I got busy completing and shipping the InsPiRing …</og:description>
<og:image>http://raspi.tv/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Thumbnail_300_HIGH.gif</og:image>
<dc:language>en-US</dc:language>
<dc:format>text/html</dc:format>
<dc:identifier>http://raspi.tv/2017/make-your-own-bike-lights-with-raspio-inspiring-day-1</dc:identifier>
