<dc:creator>alex</dc:creator>
<og:type>article</og:type>
<og:title>How to ask for (and receive) technical help on the internet</og:title>
<og:url>http://raspi.tv/2017/how-to-ask-for-and-receive-technical-help-on-the-internet</og:url>
<og:description>The internet is a great place to find out how to do things. You can often find a ‘recipe’ for precisely what you want to do or a how-to article to solve your exact problem. But even if …</og:description>
<og:image>http://raspi.tv/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/How-to-get-technical-help.thumbnail.jpg</og:image>
<dc:language>en-US</dc:language>
<dc:format>text/html</dc:format>
<dc:identifier>http://raspi.tv/2017/how-to-ask-for-and-receive-technical-help-on-the-internet</dc:identifier>
