<dc:creator>alex</dc:creator>
<og:type>article</og:type>
<og:title>How to do SMT Surface Mount Soldering by hand</og:title>
<og:url>http://raspi.tv/2017/how-to-do-smt-surface-mount-soldering-by-hand</og:url>
<og:description>I usually assemble my own prototype PCBs in my workshop. For traditional through-hole technology (THT) and large surface mount (SMT) this is a straightforward matter with no special equipment requi…</og:description>
<og:image>http://raspi.tv/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Surface-Mount-Soldering-thumb.jpg</og:image>
