&lt;div class=&quot;robots-nocontent sd-block sd-social sd-social-official sd-sharing&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3 class=&quot;sd-title&quot;&gt;Share this:&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
</description>
<pubDate>Tue, 31 Jan 2017 08:48:55 +0000</pubDate>
<dc:creator>alex</dc:creator>
<og:type>article</og:type>
<og:title>How to use external antenna on Wemos D1 mini pro – surface mount rework video</og:title>
<og:url>http://raspi.tv/2017/how-to-use-external-antenna-on-wemos-d1-mini-pro-surface-mount-rework-video</og:url>
<og:description>In my previous blog post I showed how I used several Wemos D1 mini to make a network of wireless temperature sensors around RasPiTV HQ. These litle boards are based on the ESP8266 microcontroller w…</og:description>
<og:image>http://raspi.tv/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Wemos-thumbnail_1500.jpg</og:image>
<dc:language>en-US</dc:language>
<dc:format>text/html</dc:format>
