<og:description>For a long time now I’ve wanted wireless temperature sensors scattered around the house and garden reporting their temperatures regularly to a central server. It’s not something I reall…</og:description>
<og:image>http://raspi.tv/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Wemos-D1-mini_thumbnail.jpg</og:image>
<dc:language>en-US</dc:language>
<dc:format>text/html</dc:format>
<dc:identifier>http://raspi.tv/2017/wireless-remote-sensing-with-wemos-d1-mini-arduino-ide-raspberry-pi-and-lighttpd-web-server</dc:identifier>
