<og:description>If you’ve been hanging around the RasPi.TV blog for a while you’ll have heard of the RasPiO Portsplus board. It’s a little PCB with the Pi’s GPIO port numbers on that you ca…</og:description>
<og:image>http://raspi.tv/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Portsplus-Picademy-cleaned-thumbnail_1500.jpg</og:image>
