<og:description>The other day I read an article on the BBC website which suggested a method to estimate your vocabulary. Essentially, you sample 20 pages of your dictionary and note down how many words you know on…</og:description>
<og:image>http://raspi.tv/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/vocab-thumbnail.jpg</og:image>
<dc:language>en-US</dc:language>
