<og:title>How to Flash an SD Card with Larger than 4GB Image – Raspbian September 2016 update</og:title>
<og:url>http://raspi.tv/2016/how-to-flash-an-sd-card-with-4gb-files-like-raspbian-september-2016-update</og:url>
<og:description>Yesterday (28 Sep 2016) a new version of Raspbian was released with a brand new skin called PIXEL. I downloaded it on my Mac and tried to unzip it in the usual way. It threw an error, so I assumed …</og:description>
<og:image>http://raspi.tv/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/flash-sd-card-greater-4GB.png</og:image>
<dc:language>en-US</dc:language>
<dc:format>text/html</dc:format>
