<og:type>article</og:type>
<og:title>Mailbag July 2016 overview of PaPirus Zero, Displayotron Hat, Wombat board, PiOT relay board, PiUPS+, Motozero, Zeroview</og:title>
<og:url>http://raspi.tv/2016/mailbag-july-2016-overview-of-papirus-zero-displayotron-hat-wombat-board-piot-relay-board-piups-motozero-zeroview</og:url>
<og:description>This time last year I did a “mailbag” video which was well received. So, with the review box filling up, I thought I’d do another. This time I’m covering seven products. I w…</og:description>
<og:image>http://raspi.tv/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Mailbag-July2016.jpg</og:image>
