<pubDate>Mon, 16 May 2016 07:59:07 +0000</pubDate>
<dc:creator>alex</dc:creator>
<og:type>article</og:type>
<og:title>Raspberry Pi Zero 1.3 with camera port</og:title>
<og:url>http://raspi.tv/2016/raspberry-pi-zero-1-3-with-camera-port</og:url>
<og:description>A new Raspberry Pi Zero with camera port is released today. It’s revision 1.3. Some power circuitry was moved and some unpopulated pads at U13 were removed to make space for the new mini came…</og:description>
<og:image>http://raspi.tv/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/PiZero1.3-thumb_1000.jpg</og:image>
<dc:language>en-US</dc:language>
<dc:format>text/html</dc:format>
<dc:identifier>http://raspi.tv/2016/raspberry-pi-zero-1-3-with-camera-port</dc:identifier>
