<og:description>I thought it would be fun to run the same tests on the new Pi cameras that I did on the original one back in May 2013. Unfortunately my first Pi camera 2.1 was faulty so I had to wait an extra day …</og:description>
<og:image>http://raspi.tv/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/4-way-pi-camera-comparison_1000.jpg</og:image>
<dc:language>en-US</dc:language>
