<dc:creator>alex</dc:creator>
<og:type>article</og:type>
<og:title>Using MCP3008 to measure temperature with GPIO Zero and RasPiO Pro Hat</og:title>
<og:url>http://raspi.tv/2016/using-mcp3008-to-measure-temperature-with-gpio-zero-and-raspio-pro-hat</og:url>
<og:description>In the previous article I showed you the GPIO Zero Experimenter’s Kit I put together to go with the RasPiO® Pro Hat. Today I’m going to give a quick overview of how to use the MCP3008 a…</og:description>
<og:image>http://raspi.tv/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/ProHat-MCP3008-TMP36c.png</og:image>
<dc:language>en-US</dc:language>
<dc:format>text/html</dc:format>
<dc:identifier>http://raspi.tv/2016/using-mcp3008-to-measure-temperature-with-gpio-zero-and-raspio-pro-hat</dc:identifier>
