<og:description>On Tuesday I had a funny thing happen. I was testing an analogue to digital converter (ADC) chip – the MCP3008 – to see how well it worked on the RasPiO® Pro Hat. I had it all wired up,…</og:description>
<og:image>http://raspi.tv/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/ExperimentersKit-thumbnail_900.jpg</og:image>
