<og:title>Always Test Everything – Twitter App Update</og:title>
<og:url>http://raspi.tv/2016/always-test-everything-twitter-app-update</og:url>
<og:description>I’m a firm believer that you should always test things in advance. It helps avoid unexpected last-minute panics when things don’t work as you expected them to. On Friday I’m going…</og:description>
<og:image>http://raspi.tv/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/twitdraw.jpg</og:image>
<dc:language>en-US</dc:language>
<dc:format>text/html</dc:format>
